- Invocations: `new Set(...)`, `cells.map(cellKey)`, `new Map()`, `neighbors(cell)`, `cellKey(n)`, `neighborCount.set(...)`, `neighborCount.get(k)`, `k.split(",")`, `.map(Number)`, `liveSet.has(k)`, `result.push(cell)`, `result.sort(...)`, `a[1] - b[1]` (subtraction is an operator, not invocation), = 12 invocations = 24
